<p>
<note n="0080003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0080003">明本譯號同異如首卷及譯號前行有法稱菩薩造五字</note>
<note n="0080004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0080004">Vajradhvaja-sūtra.</note>
<note n="0080005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0080005">垂＝乘【明】</note>
<note n="0080006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0080006">幡＝旛【明】</note>
<note n="0081001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0081001">茵＝裀【明】</note>
<note n="0082001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0082001">止＝上【明】</note>
<note n="0082002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0082002">憂＝幽【明】</note>
<note n="0082003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0082003">Śīlapāramitāyaṃ saddharma-parigraho nāma dvitīyaḥ paricchedaḥ.</note>
<note n="0082004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0082004">梵. Vīradatta-paripṛcchā.</note>
